{"tid":891183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打電話要她矇眼脫光 怪男假裝是男友到府做愛","createTime":"2018-11-06T01:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T01:47:23.000Z","uid":64191,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f32b7f43a86f886beb293c98614aa88a207930d3","tid":891183,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕北市一名男子隨機打電話給女生，假裝是她的男友，藉機與女子發生關係，這種手法聽起來相當荒謬，但男子真的成功騙了一名女子，事後遭正牌男友爆打。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報導，一名40多歲張姓男子於去年7月間，用隨機打電話的方式聯繫到一名住在高雄的女子，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">女子男友在外地工作，兩人很少見面，張男竟然假裝是她男友，甚至提出要女子矇著眼睛在家等他，想要與女子大戰一場的要求，女子聽了乖乖照辦，兩人遂發生關係。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，張男食髓知味，但第二次女子並未戴上眼罩，結果看到是張男假扮男友，不禁崩潰，想辦法將張男留置家中並請男友回家，事後張男遭正牌男友爆打。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，地檢署指出，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">案件中張男並未暴力脅迫或違反女子意願，不構成強制性交罪，<br />\n此外，由於被害人並非已婚狀態，也不構成「詐術性交」，處分不起訴</span>。反而張男控告正牌男友傷害，事證明確，正牌男友被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2603205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2603205&d=eG%2BH%2BmnwJydb3jju8aYqiZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ec3e410b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2603205&h=fe1c1265\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2603205</a>"},{"pid":"c756cfdb37858285bdb7821914bbcd68a73e70f2","tid":891183,"uid":108993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:42:22.000Z","msg":"變咗G自己唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cea6c8eeba6c57eaae2ab4c351c98ef9d78d1b3","tid":891183,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"00d6653db035ac3e13242ef9fc9a56b4393b05a4","tid":891183,"uid":62367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:44:00.000Z","msg":"帽撚到咁都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不概地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b5dec5835688047937088b9a43d7a81ce89fae","tid":891183,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"點解會識路到府呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c2d8ddf0e008f4caac7d49ade48ee4e9a6bf1d","tid":891183,"uid":101805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"隨機打點知地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c39974575e816afc383fa99c3dec4d9a233148","tid":891183,"uid":2035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"有冇可能第一次唔知"},{"pid":"1d9a0eba0a86368eb2c4afb532e329885e366849","tid":891183,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"想辦法將張男留置家中並請男友回家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">How?</span></span>"}]}